commit_message:
Merge pull request #6 from bioinformed/master

Many tweaks, cleanups and fixes

Update README.md

Flesh out README with better information about configuration file format and requirements
Add new caller funcs with less lower qual cutoffs
Fix GT mod code for missing alt alleles, we now ignore them
Add simulated fastqs and truth VCFs
Update tests, change filename defaults for generated fastqs
Add half-call remover, along with testing code
Fix filename parsing for vcf batching
Sort calls from new freebayes version
Add in workaround for GATK error regarding sorted VCFs
Fix bug when parsing GTs from input VCF
Watch out for empty vcfs to avoid pysam bug
Better plotting for result parsing, watch for None alleles when comparing

Merge pull request #5 from goranrakocevic/master

added setup.py
Move existing callers, etc to internal package
Move existing callers, etc to internal package
Update configuration files to have absolute paths for plugins
Fix weird import issue in sim package
Refactoring caller/normalizer/comparator specific code to new plugin architecture, experimental support for independent generation of fastqs
Emit variant quality per caller with results
Apparently read.cigartuples can be None sometimes
Add random str to batch file names to prevent clobbers
Add varscan path to linux conf
VarScan2, fix bug handling comparator errors
Flag variants with comparator errors instead of raising exceptions
Result analyzer stratifies by insertion / deletion size
Fix MNP processing, update parser script to support a few more analysis types
Change result output format to json
Update result parsing script for new output style
Allow additional SNPs to be added near input variants
Better support for simulated vars with multiple alts
Updates for new version of vgraph, logging, doc
More fixes for batch processing, add no_et code for gatk if key file is present
Big refactoring for batch processing, but seems to work now
Added Kevins partitioning script, modified to keep vars in input order
Fix bug causing homozygous output only

Separated out the fastq creation from alignment.
Adjust hap.py to still examine non-passing variants
Fix hap.py comparator, better code for flagging tmp dirs to preserve
Additional result type for finding extra variants
No partial credit, report perfect match only if tp>0 and fp and fn == 0
Refuse to change GT in multi-alt VCFs
Fix up identification of vgraph / vcfeval mismatches in parsing
Fix issue where vgraph didnt return a valid result for empty caller vcf
Fix for removing partial match result type
Fix parsing for new normalization scheme, add vcfallelicprimitives and gatk leftalign as normalization method
Refactor to have separate normalization and comparison functions
vcfeval ignores filter status of variants now
Suppress output of vcfeval to stdout
New zygosity comparing mechanism, still in testing
Fix bug in new gt parsing scheme
Fix issue where incorrect_genotype could be reported as no variants found
Fix issue where read length could differ from base qualities length
Fix for missing read issue in bam simulation
Fix serious bug in batching code
Detect variant genotype mismatches, process variants in batches for test_callers
Sort keys, better output in parse_caller_output
different variant types in gen vcf

New modules for testing variant calling
